quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  104,1,"Loza ho an'izay mpanendrikendrika sy mpifosa !"
  104,2,"Izay nanangona harena sy nanisa izany."
  104,3,"Mihevitra izy fa ny harena dia hampaharitra azy mandrakizay."
  104,4,"Tsia ! Tsy maintsy hatsipiko ao anaty Afo izy."
  104,5,"Moa fantatrao va izany Afo izany ?"
  104,6,"Izany dia Afon'I Allah miredareda !"
  104,7,"izay miantefa hatrany am-po."
  104,8,"Ka hanepotra azy ireo."
  104,9,"Ao anaty fefy mijoalajoala no sady mivelatra."
